creator: Flick Inc
descriptionHtml:
VAULT is a new creator platform from the co-founders of FanDuel that uses the power of Web 3.0 to unlock the next generation of fan experiences.

Built on the Solana blockchain, the VAULT platform allows creators to curate a vault of content — music, videos, photos, messages, VIP invitations, and more — that can only be unlocked by the holders of a key.
descriptionShort: VAULT is a creator platform where fans unlock access to exclusive content.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
• VAULT now has video!
• View details of the Vaults you can access, including descriptions and holder benefits.
• Minor bug fixes and performance improvements.
